        public void write(org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.data.api.YangInstanceIdentifier path,
                  org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.data.api.schema.NormalizedNode<?,?> data)
        已过时。 
        从接口复制的说明: DOMStoreWriteTransaction
        Store a provided data at specified path. This acts as a add / replace operation, which is to say that whole subtree will be replaced by specified path.

        If you need add or merge of current object with specified use DOMStoreWriteTransaction.merge(YangInstanceIdentifier, NormalizedNode).

        指定者:
        write 在接口中 DOMStoreWriteTransaction
        参数:
        path - the path to write
        data - data object to be written
